---
const pains = [
  {
    title: 'Pretty, but quiet.',
    body: 'Your site looks polished but the inquiries never come. Beautiful design without conversion architecture is just expensive decoration.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Slow to load, fast to lose.',
    body: 'A 3-second load time costs you 40% of mobile visitors before they ever see your hero. Most sites bleed traffic at the door.',
  },
  {
    title: 'No clear next action.',
    body: 'Visitors land, scroll, and leave because the page does not tell them what to do next. Action paths beat aesthetics every time.',
  },
  {
    title: 'A brochure, not a funnel.',
    body: 'Your site explains who you are but never asks for the lead. Pages should move people from curious to committed -section by section.',
  },
];
---

<section class="bg-white py-24 md:py-36">
  <div class="container-x">
    <div class="grid items-start gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-20">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:sticky lg:top-28 lg:self-start">
        <span class="eyebrow">
          <span class="h-px w-6 bg-gold"></span>
          The real problem
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-medium leading-[1.05] tracking-tight md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.25rem]">
          Most websites underperform for the same four reasons.
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink md:text-xl">
          A website's job isn't traffic. It's conversion.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-ink/65 md:text-lg">
          The web is full of agencies selling templates dressed up as design. We build the structure underneath -the part that decides whether a visitor becomes a lead.
        </p>

        <blockquote class="relative rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-[#FBF8EF] p-8 md:p-10">
          <span class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-4 left-8 font-display text-7xl leading-none text-gold/20 select-none">&ldquo;</span>
          <p class="relative text-base leading-relaxed text-ink md:text-lg">
            A site that wins awards but loses leads is a failed site. We design every section with one question: <span class="font-semibold text-ink">what action does this page need to drive?</span>
          </p>
          <footer class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="h-px w-8 bg-gold"></span>
            <div>
              <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Jack He</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-ink/50">Owner, Rumeira</div>
            </div>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
        {pains.map((p, i) => (
          <article class="group rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white p-7 transition-colors duration-300 hover:border-gold/40 md:p-9">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
              <span class="font-display text-sm font-medium text-gold">{String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
              <div class="flex-1">
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-medium leading-tight md:text-2xl">{p.title}</h3>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink/65 md:text-lg">{p.body}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
